      "description": "Hi everyone! I'm looking to find a new home for my absolute favorite ride. She\u2019s been incredibly reliable and is still looking sharp and running like a dream! I\u2019ve really taken care of this car and it\u2019s served me so well on every trip. It's a solid, dependable choice that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you're interested!",
