    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered icon. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features a healthy dual-VANOS system and crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. It sits on a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis' primary structural weak point, and utilizes a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. While it shows honest signs of use, its performance envelope remains sharp, offering the tactile feedback and analog engagement synonymous with the M-division's peak era.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
