    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with a well-loved driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation and premium audio system\u2014operate as they did on day one. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a strict adherence to its maintenance schedule. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. It has been garage-kept and frequently detailed, ensuring that it remains a standout example of its model. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this car is ready for immediate enjoyment without any pending maintenance needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
